1.1
log
@Update to freetype 2.4.12. tested by many during t2k13. Thanks.
@
text
@d6 1
a6 1
<title>FreeType-2.4.12 API Reference</title>
d38 1
a38 1
<center><h1>FreeType-2.4.12 API Reference</h1></center>
d55 2
a56 2
<p>Thanks to Adobe, which contributed a new hinting (and parsing) engine, an application can select between &lsquo;freetype&rsquo; and &lsquo;adobe&rsquo;.</p>
<p>Right now, the default engine is &lsquo;freetype&rsquo;. However, this will change: After a certain time of intensive testing it is planned to make &lsquo;adobe&rsquo; the default due to its superior rendering results.</p>
